title: Tiny Desk Contest Top Shelf: Our Favorite 2021 Entries, Episode 6
description: Before we announce this year's winner, we're asking our judges to share their favorite entries in a weekly livestreamed series. In this episode, last year's winner, Linda Diaz, shares her picks.
